{
  "texts": [
    "It has been put to use in GAN training.",
    "To prevent GAN discriminator catastrophic forgetting, SS tasks were created.",
    "This paper analyses how SS tasks affect generator learning.",
    "From the analysis, we uncover SS task difficulties that a mode-collapsed generator should be allowed to shine.",
    "It provides fresh SS challenges built around a minimax game with many classes."
  ]
}